{"tid":2454771,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"自護D軍備咁多種類，點解會輸","createTime":"2021-03-20T13:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T14:55:30.000Z","uid":18012,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"2aa8c19a632b8bcc33af1264cfa44c39c4319d8d","tid":2454771,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/3471c3/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/vm-dabude.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2F3471c3%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fvm-dabude.jpg&h=9c6224cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n○多柏戴級(Dobday class，ダブデ)陸上戰艦<br />\n<br />\n裝備類別：陸上戰艦<br />\n初次列裝時間：0079年<br />\n武裝：雙聯裝主炮x2，雙聯裝副炮x2<br />\n機械設定：大河原邦男<br />\n出處：機動戰士高達<br />\n重要人物：馬&bull;克貝（搭乘）<br />\n簡介：<br />\n  自護軍的重型陸上戰艦，作為高級軍官的指揮部使用。底部裝設巨大的履帶，可以高速行進；在發射主炮時則由接地架將艦體固定在地上。其後部格納庫中可儲存核彈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/eb4442/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/dodaiys.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2Feb4442%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fdodaiys.jpg&h=ab627894&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/5ca209/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/vm-dodai.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2F5ca209%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fvm-dodai.jpg&h=9fb5f3be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n○德戴YS(Dodai YS，ドダイYS)<br />\n<br />\n裝備類別：MS運輸艇<br />\n初次列裝時間：0079年<br />\n武裝：導彈發射器x8<br />\n出處：機動戰士高達<br />\n簡介：<br />\n  德戴YS是德戴GA的簡單改進型，其加強了機體背部結構，並加裝了固定MS腳部的掛鈎，利用德戴GA的大載重，用來搭載MS，使之能踩在本機上面，在 空中快速運輸及作戰，大大提高了MS的機動性和戰鬥力。在一年戰爭中，作為MS的飛行載具，德戴YS相當活躍，亦取得了可觀的戰果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/cc25b4/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/gaw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2Fcc25b4%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fgaw.jpg&h=2969c9d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/d4cb02/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/vm-gau3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2Fd4cb02%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fvm-gau3.gif&h=f91a10e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n○加烏級(Gaw，ガウ)攻擊空母<br />\n<br />\n裝備類別：攻擊空母<br />\n初次列裝時間：0079年3月<br />\n全長：147.4米<br />\n翼展：159.4米<br />\n全高：72.4米<br />\n滿載重量：690.4噸<br />\n推進系統：原子噴射引擎x18<br />\n武裝：雙聯裝MEGA粒子炮x3、防空機炮數基<br />\n搭載MS：3機<br />\n搭載戰機：8架<br />\n機械設定：大河原邦男<br />\n出處：機動戰士高達、高達第08MS小隊<br />\n重要人物：卡爾瑪&bull;紮比<br />\n簡介：<br />\n  自護軍因應地球的作戰環境及自軍的局限，在地球降下作戰之後即著手開發加烏級攻擊空母。3至5月間，加烏級陸續列裝，戰爭期間生產總數在20架以上； 18台原子噴射引擎使該型空母具有強勁的出力和升力，其巨大的機身也使它履行機動兵器母機的任務同時，亦作為很優秀的戰略轟炸機參戰。這種高速、高續航 力、大裝載量的巨型戰機在一年戰爭期間戰功卓著，在很多時候它也被高級軍官當作指揮部使用。<br />\n  在富野的高達小說中，加烏級被設定為一種宇宙空母。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/d95779/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/madangler.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2Fd95779%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fmadangler.jpg&h=bff17a7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n○魔鯊級(Mad Angler class，マッドアングラー)潛水母艦<br />\n<br />\n裝備類別：潛水母艦<br />\n初次列裝時間：0079年10月<br />\n同型艦：魔鯊、茲埃<br />\n搭載MS：9機，水中型MA 1機、6艘海矛偵察艇、3架偵察機<br />\n機械設定：富野喜幸(設計)、大河原邦男(修正)<br />\n出處：機動戰士高達<br />\n重要人物：夏亞&bull;阿茲納布（搭乘）<br />\n簡介：<br />\n  魔鯊級潛水母艦的前身系為聯邦海軍建造的大型導彈攻擊潛艇。加利福尼亞基地被攻陷後，自護軍俘獲了這兩艘正在建造的潛艇，並將之改建為&ldquo;魔鯊&rdquo;級潛水 母艦。一號艦&ldquo;魔鯊&rdquo;於10月10日建成，並於10月30日作為特殊潛水艦隊（&ldquo;魔鯊艦隊&rdquo;）的旗艦配備在北大西洋。魔鯊級一共建造了兩艘，另一艘名為 &ldquo;茲埃(ズアイ)&rdquo;；另有資料說一共建造了8艘，但此一數據不足取信。<br />\n  &ldquo;魔鯊(Mad Angler)&rdquo;一名亦可意譯為&ldquo;瘋狂射水魚&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"05c5a3a5e48cb98d7157f33034b628a9297bf5b5","tid":2454771,"uid":312193,"like":21,"dislike":4,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:05:53.000Z","msg":"因為石頭製造"},{"pid":"e9cb76db2beabb199055d0ec68e08e92473778a6","tid":2454771,"uid":18012,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:06:23.000Z","msg":"海陸空都齊晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解會輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5f702a3016066520715975a5a0154e25b307a5","tid":2454771,"uid":242102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:06:33.000Z","msg":"劇情殺"},{"pid":"732c88a667d9346967b4bc87630d62050710ed77","tid":2454771,"uid":256205,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:07:25.000Z","msg":"認真答你<br />\n高達太屈機<br />\n應該話<br />\n阿寶太屈機"},{"pid":"c70747a84874a4f5f109b769479bde2b01f32cd0","tid":2454771,"uid":103678,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:14:10.000Z","msg":"就係因為又多又雜<br />\n零件唔統一咁咪增加成本囉<br />\n加上聯邦係玩人海+資源<br />\n自護比人睇穿底牌就輸"},{"pid":"80b5f8f88f4e139f9fa82fc004974e12cef3ae8c","tid":2454771,"uid":177089,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:32:45.000Z","msg":"德國都好多裝修"},{"pid":"9af300e9f3c9f12b0c8e839d8334ea27c2761256","tid":2454771,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80b5f8f88f4e139f9fa82fc004974e12cef3ae8c","tid":2454771,"uid":177089,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:32:45.000Z","msg":"德國都好多裝修"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:33:00.000Z","msg":"備"},{"pid":"cf172c6575237a9231886717b229203001feada7","tid":2454771,"uid":17443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:35:15.000Z","msg":"石頭....腳..."},{"pid":"0a6dc425e2f247dfc9a6bb2c120234921da5132b","tid":2454771,"uid":35696,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:38:45.000Z","msg":"因為聯邦用61式同鐵球海都浸得死自護"},{"pid":"9624ff8a2b7b29a75a7aafcb85d8bc5d65961581","tid":2454771,"uid":83009,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:38:59.000Z","msg":"機械既野&hellip;"},{"pid":"40625c3a059eab65e6a3a5c503da150cca089673","tid":2454771,"uid":69311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:39:55.000Z","msg":"因為無主角光環同係反派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68974055fbba7d4c2492c1dd369acda48c54bc5a","tid":2454771,"uid":34197,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"c70747a84874a4f5f109b769479bde2b01f32cd0","tid":2454771,"uid":103678,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:14:10.000Z","msg":"就係因為又多又雜<br />\n零件唔統一咁咪增加成本囉<br />\n加上聯邦係玩人海+資源<br />\n自護比人睇穿底牌就輸"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:41:31.000Z","msg":"正想講呢樣<br />\n零件唔共通係死症嚟,拖慢晒戰線補給,如果你手上咁冇晒嗰款parts,隔離左右又冇同型號機,就分分鐘要係冇雷公咁遠咁運嚟,未運到嚟都俾人炸死咗<br />\n好似吉姆咁,只要唔係炸駕駛艙或者變成灰,幾部傷唔同parts嘅吉姆拆啲完好嘅parts出嚟就可以直接砌返部完整嘅嚟用,可以係短時間變返即戰力已經差天共地"},{"pid":"11c75d095db9002d7dc9c867e003e556681d9dd2","tid":2454771,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"732c88a667d9346967b4bc87630d62050710ed77","tid":2454771,"uid":256205,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:07:25.000Z","msg":"認真答你<br />\n高達太屈機<br />\n應該話<br />\n阿寶太屈機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:42:37.000Z","msg":"阿寶拖時間好關鍵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4627bc72c28859aeb63453179b2af63fb48837","tid":2454771,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40625c3a059eab65e6a3a5c503da150cca089673","tid":2454771,"uid":69311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:39:55.000Z","msg":"因為無主角光環同係反派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf57b9bff87f64ac40ca6667de95289ed98c52ab","tid":2454771,"uid":3441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:48:06.000Z","msg":"Experienced soldiers mostly die in early stage of the war."},{"pid":"7c2bd0d95c4a5b433d2d30baef0095051f56fbff","tid":2454771,"uid":261873,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:49:43.000Z","msg":"因為套動畫叫高達"},{"pid":"c6a97ab9c2aa931e6a7610320e1f3e49520f684e","tid":2454771,"uid":310648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aa8c19a632b8bcc33af1264cfa44c39c4319d8d","tid":2454771,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/3471c3/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/vm-dabude.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2F3471c3%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fvm-dabude.jpg&h=9c6224cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n○多柏戴級(Dobday class，ダブデ)陸上戰艦<br />\n<br />\n裝備類別：陸上戰艦<br />\n初次列裝時間：0079年<br />\n武裝：雙聯裝主炮x2，雙聯裝副炮x2<br />\n機械設定：大河原邦男<br />\n出處：機動戰士高達<br />\n重要人物：馬&bull;克貝（搭乘）<br />\n簡介：<br />\n  自護軍的重型陸上戰艦，作為高級軍官的指揮部使用。底部裝設巨大的履帶，可以高速行進；在發射主炮時則由接地架將艦體固定在地上。其後部格納庫中可儲存核彈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/eb4442/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/dodaiys.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2Feb4442%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fdodaiys.jpg&h=ab627894&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/5ca209/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/vm-dodai.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2F5ca209%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fvm-dodai.jpg&h=9fb5f3be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n○德戴YS(Dodai YS，ドダイYS)<br />\n<br />\n裝備類別：MS運輸艇<br />\n初次列裝時間：0079年<br />\n武裝：導彈發射器x8<br />\n出處：機動戰士高達<br />\n簡介：<br />\n  德戴YS是德戴GA的簡單改進型，其加強了機體背部結構，並加裝了固定MS腳部的掛鈎，利用德戴GA的大載重，用來搭載MS，使之能踩在本機上面，在 空中快速運輸及作戰，大大提高了MS的機動性和戰鬥力。在一年戰爭中，作為MS的飛行載具，德戴YS相當活躍，亦取得了可觀的戰果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/cc25b4/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/gaw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2Fcc25b4%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fgaw.jpg&h=2969c9d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/d4cb02/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/vm-gau3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2Fd4cb02%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fvm-gau3.gif&h=f91a10e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n○加烏級(Gaw，ガウ)攻擊空母<br />\n<br />\n裝備類別：攻擊空母<br />\n初次列裝時間：0079年3月<br />\n全長：147.4米<br />\n翼展：159.4米<br />\n全高：72.4米<br />\n滿載重量：690.4噸<br />\n推進系統：原子噴射引擎x18<br />\n武裝：雙聯裝MEGA粒子炮x3、防空機炮數基<br />\n搭載MS：3機<br />\n搭載戰機：8架<br />\n機械設定：大河原邦男<br />\n出處：機動戰士高達、高達第08MS小隊<br />\n重要人物：卡爾瑪&bull;紮比<br />\n簡介：<br />\n  自護軍因應地球的作戰環境及自軍的局限，在地球降下作戰之後即著手開發加烏級攻擊空母。3至5月間，加烏級陸續列裝，戰爭期間生產總數在20架以上； 18台原子噴射引擎使該型空母具有強勁的出力和升力，其巨大的機身也使它履行機動兵器母機的任務同時，亦作為很優秀的戰略轟炸機參戰。這種高速、高續航 力、大裝載量的巨型戰機在一年戰爭期間戰功卓著，在很多時候它也被高級軍官當作指揮部使用。<br />\n  在富野的高達小說中，加烏級被設定為一種宇宙空母。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/d95779/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/madangler.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2Fd95779%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fmadangler.jpg&h=bff17a7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n○魔鯊級(Mad Angler class，マッドアングラー)潛水母艦<br />\n<br />\n裝備類別：潛水母艦<br />\n初次列裝時間：0079年10月<br />\n同型艦：魔鯊、茲埃<br />\n搭載MS：9機，水中型MA 1機、6艘海矛偵察艇、3架偵察機<br />\n機械設定：富野喜幸(設計)、大河原邦男(修正)<br />\n出處：機動戰士高達<br />\n重要人物：夏亞&bull;阿茲納布（搭乘）<br />\n簡介：<br />\n  魔鯊級潛水母艦的前身系為聯邦海軍建造的大型導彈攻擊潛艇。加利福尼亞基地被攻陷後，自護軍俘獲了這兩艘正在建造的潛艇，並將之改建為&ldquo;魔鯊&rdquo;級潛水 母艦。一號艦&ldquo;魔鯊&rdquo;於10月10日建成，並於10月30日作為特殊潛水艦隊（&ldquo;魔鯊艦隊&rdquo;）的旗艦配備在北大西洋。魔鯊級一共建造了兩艘，另一艘名為 &ldquo;茲埃(ズアイ)&rdquo;；另有資料說一共建造了8艘，但此一數據不足取信。<br />\n  &ldquo;魔鯊(Mad Angler)&rdquo;一名亦可意譯為&ldquo;瘋狂射水魚&rdquo;。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T14:02:24.000Z","msg":"啲嘢太花巧(就連MS好多試作/實驗機)量產唔到<br />\n資源又唔夠<br />\n再俾大量吉姆同鐵球圍毆<br />\n點打呀大佬"},{"pid":"9d1cfa7a00aae384d6b3b55d0ef1eae68359de9e","tid":2454771,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9cb76db2beabb199055d0ec68e08e92473778a6","tid":2454771,"uid":18012,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:06:23.000Z","msg":"海陸空都齊晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解會輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T14:36:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死柒頭"},{"pid":"cc01125fbd33bf0d4a859ffe873f2b9b0f89a5d0","tid":2454771,"uid":312130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T14:44:23.000Z","msg":"石頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd794a75d4c6cb5aa4493bb7deafdb2af48cd4b","tid":2454771,"uid":4493,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:11:48.000Z","msg":"原著就係參考二次大戰<br />\n自護同德國一樣好多先進武器<br />\n但係就係因為種類多 成本高又補給困難<br />\n對比對面大量M4/GM 後期就算一對一贏都冇用"},{"pid":"a3377735b7cc80e8f42d6f5a4da7ac3dbfa0d32e","tid":2454771,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf57b9bff87f64ac40ca6667de95289ed98c52ab","tid":2454771,"uid":3441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:48:06.000Z","msg":"Experienced soldiers mostly die in early stage of the war."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:12:52.000Z","msg":"阿寶殺撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95bb936f5f5eb10f6147e33da1799d6137315960","tid":2454771,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6a97ab9c2aa931e6a7610320e1f3e49520f684e","tid":2454771,"uid":310648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aa8c19a632b8bcc33af1264cfa44c39c4319d8d","tid":2454771,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/3471c3/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/vm-dabude.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2F3471c3%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fvm-dabude.jpg&h=9c6224cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n○多柏戴級(Dobday class，ダブデ)陸上戰艦<br />\n<br />\n裝備類別：陸上戰艦<br />\n初次列裝時間：0079年<br />\n武裝：雙聯裝主炮x2，雙聯裝副炮x2<br />\n機械設定：大河原邦男<br />\n出處：機動戰士高達<br />\n重要人物：馬&bull;克貝（搭乘）<br />\n簡介：<br />\n  自護軍的重型陸上戰艦，作為高級軍官的指揮部使用。底部裝設巨大的履帶，可以高速行進；在發射主炮時則由接地架將艦體固定在地上。其後部格納庫中可儲存核彈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/eb4442/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/dodaiys.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2Feb4442%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fdodaiys.jpg&h=ab627894&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/5ca209/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/vm-dodai.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2F5ca209%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fvm-dodai.jpg&h=9fb5f3be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n○德戴YS(Dodai YS，ドダイYS)<br />\n<br />\n裝備類別：MS運輸艇<br />\n初次列裝時間：0079年<br />\n武裝：導彈發射器x8<br />\n出處：機動戰士高達<br />\n簡介：<br />\n  德戴YS是德戴GA的簡單改進型，其加強了機體背部結構，並加裝了固定MS腳部的掛鈎，利用德戴GA的大載重，用來搭載MS，使之能踩在本機上面，在 空中快速運輸及作戰，大大提高了MS的機動性和戰鬥力。在一年戰爭中，作為MS的飛行載具，德戴YS相當活躍，亦取得了可觀的戰果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/cc25b4/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/gaw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2Fcc25b4%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fgaw.jpg&h=2969c9d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/d4cb02/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/vm-gau3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2Fd4cb02%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fvm-gau3.gif&h=f91a10e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n○加烏級(Gaw，ガウ)攻擊空母<br />\n<br />\n裝備類別：攻擊空母<br />\n初次列裝時間：0079年3月<br />\n全長：147.4米<br />\n翼展：159.4米<br />\n全高：72.4米<br />\n滿載重量：690.4噸<br />\n推進系統：原子噴射引擎x18<br />\n武裝：雙聯裝MEGA粒子炮x3、防空機炮數基<br />\n搭載MS：3機<br />\n搭載戰機：8架<br />\n機械設定：大河原邦男<br />\n出處：機動戰士高達、高達第08MS小隊<br />\n重要人物：卡爾瑪&bull;紮比<br />\n簡介：<br />\n  自護軍因應地球的作戰環境及自軍的局限，在地球降下作戰之後即著手開發加烏級攻擊空母。3至5月間，加烏級陸續列裝，戰爭期間生產總數在20架以上； 18台原子噴射引擎使該型空母具有強勁的出力和升力，其巨大的機身也使它履行機動兵器母機的任務同時，亦作為很優秀的戰略轟炸機參戰。這種高速、高續航 力、大裝載量的巨型戰機在一年戰爭期間戰功卓著，在很多時候它也被高級軍官當作指揮部使用。<br />\n  在富野的高達小說中，加烏級被設定為一種宇宙空母。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/d95779/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/madangler.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2Fd95779%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fmadangler.jpg&h=bff17a7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n○魔鯊級(Mad Angler class，マッドアングラー)潛水母艦<br />\n<br />\n裝備類別：潛水母艦<br />\n初次列裝時間：0079年10月<br />\n同型艦：魔鯊、茲埃<br />\n搭載MS：9機，水中型MA 1機、6艘海矛偵察艇、3架偵察機<br />\n機械設定：富野喜幸(設計)、大河原邦男(修正)<br />\n出處：機動戰士高達<br />\n重要人物：夏亞&bull;阿茲納布（搭乘）<br />\n簡介：<br />\n  魔鯊級潛水母艦的前身系為聯邦海軍建造的大型導彈攻擊潛艇。加利福尼亞基地被攻陷後，自護軍俘獲了這兩艘正在建造的潛艇，並將之改建為&ldquo;魔鯊&rdquo;級潛水 母艦。一號艦&ldquo;魔鯊&rdquo;於10月10日建成，並於10月30日作為特殊潛水艦隊（&ldquo;魔鯊艦隊&rdquo;）的旗艦配備在北大西洋。魔鯊級一共建造了兩艘，另一艘名為 &ldquo;茲埃(ズアイ)&rdquo;；另有資料說一共建造了8艘，但此一數據不足取信。<br />\n  &ldquo;魔鯊(Mad Angler)&rdquo;一名亦可意譯為&ldquo;瘋狂射水魚&rdquo;。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T14:02:24.000Z","msg":"啲嘢太花巧(就連MS好多試作/實驗機)量產唔到<br />\n資源又唔夠<br />\n再俾大量吉姆同鐵球圍毆<br />\n點打呀大佬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:13:46.000Z","msg":"睇親動畫都係新型機秒殺鐵球 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505c7bf8d5e9943d35437a2880d01521becdfa3e","tid":2454771,"uid":134174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95bb936f5f5eb10f6147e33da1799d6137315960","tid":2454771,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6a97ab9c2aa931e6a7610320e1f3e49520f684e","tid":2454771,"uid":310648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aa8c19a632b8bcc33af1264cfa44c39c4319d8d","tid":2454771,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/3471c3/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/vm-dabude.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2F3471c3%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fvm-dabude.jpg&h=9c6224cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n○多柏戴級(Dobday class，ダブデ)陸上戰艦<br />\n<br />\n裝備類別：陸上戰艦<br />\n初次列裝時間：0079年<br />\n武裝：雙聯裝主炮x2，雙聯裝副炮x2<br />\n機械設定：大河原邦男<br />\n出處：機動戰士高達<br />\n重要人物：馬&bull;克貝（搭乘）<br />\n簡介：<br />\n  自護軍的重型陸上戰艦，作為高級軍官的指揮部使用。底部裝設巨大的履帶，可以高速行進；在發射主炮時則由接地架將艦體固定在地上。其後部格納庫中可儲存核彈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/eb4442/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/dodaiys.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2Feb4442%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fdodaiys.jpg&h=ab627894&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/5ca209/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/vm-dodai.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2F5ca209%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fvm-dodai.jpg&h=9fb5f3be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n○德戴YS(Dodai YS，ドダイYS)<br />\n<br />\n裝備類別：MS運輸艇<br />\n初次列裝時間：0079年<br />\n武裝：導彈發射器x8<br />\n出處：機動戰士高達<br />\n簡介：<br />\n  德戴YS是德戴GA的簡單改進型，其加強了機體背部結構，並加裝了固定MS腳部的掛鈎，利用德戴GA的大載重，用來搭載MS，使之能踩在本機上面，在 空中快速運輸及作戰，大大提高了MS的機動性和戰鬥力。在一年戰爭中，作為MS的飛行載具，德戴YS相當活躍，亦取得了可觀的戰果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/cc25b4/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/gaw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2Fcc25b4%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fgaw.jpg&h=2969c9d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/d4cb02/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/vm-gau3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2Fd4cb02%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fvm-gau3.gif&h=f91a10e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n○加烏級(Gaw，ガウ)攻擊空母<br />\n<br />\n裝備類別：攻擊空母<br />\n初次列裝時間：0079年3月<br />\n全長：147.4米<br />\n翼展：159.4米<br />\n全高：72.4米<br />\n滿載重量：690.4噸<br />\n推進系統：原子噴射引擎x18<br />\n武裝：雙聯裝MEGA粒子炮x3、防空機炮數基<br />\n搭載MS：3機<br />\n搭載戰機：8架<br />\n機械設定：大河原邦男<br />\n出處：機動戰士高達、高達第08MS小隊<br />\n重要人物：卡爾瑪&bull;紮比<br />\n簡介：<br />\n  自護軍因應地球的作戰環境及自軍的局限，在地球降下作戰之後即著手開發加烏級攻擊空母。3至5月間，加烏級陸續列裝，戰爭期間生產總數在20架以上； 18台原子噴射引擎使該型空母具有強勁的出力和升力，其巨大的機身也使它履行機動兵器母機的任務同時，亦作為很優秀的戰略轟炸機參戰。這種高速、高續航 力、大裝載量的巨型戰機在一年戰爭期間戰功卓著，在很多時候它也被高級軍官當作指揮部使用。<br />\n  在富野的高達小說中，加烏級被設定為一種宇宙空母。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uwants.com/t/d95779/f/800x0/http://i61.photobucket.com/albums/h48/samsongoh/madangler.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.uwants.com%2Ft%2Fd95779%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi61.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh48%2Fsamsongoh%2Fmadangler.jpg&h=bff17a7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n○魔鯊級(Mad Angler class，マッドアングラー)潛水母艦<br />\n<br />\n裝備類別：潛水母艦<br />\n初次列裝時間：0079年10月<br />\n同型艦：魔鯊、茲埃<br />\n搭載MS：9機，水中型MA 1機、6艘海矛偵察艇、3架偵察機<br />\n機械設定：富野喜幸(設計)、大河原邦男(修正)<br />\n出處：機動戰士高達<br />\n重要人物：夏亞&bull;阿茲納布（搭乘）<br />\n簡介：<br />\n  魔鯊級潛水母艦的前身系為聯邦海軍建造的大型導彈攻擊潛艇。加利福尼亞基地被攻陷後，自護軍俘獲了這兩艘正在建造的潛艇，並將之改建為&ldquo;魔鯊&rdquo;級潛水 母艦。一號艦&ldquo;魔鯊&rdquo;於10月10日建成，並於10月30日作為特殊潛水艦隊（&ldquo;魔鯊艦隊&rdquo;）的旗艦配備在北大西洋。魔鯊級一共建造了兩艘，另一艘名為 &ldquo;茲埃(ズアイ)&rdquo;；另有資料說一共建造了8艘，但此一數據不足取信。<br />\n  &ldquo;魔鯊(Mad Angler)&rdquo;一名亦可意譯為&ldquo;瘋狂射水魚&rdquo;。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T14:02:24.000Z","msg":"啲嘢太花巧(就連MS好多試作/實驗機)量產唔到<br />\n資源又唔夠<br />\n再俾大量吉姆同鐵球圍毆<br />\n點打呀大佬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:13:46.000Z","msg":"睇親動畫都係新型機秒殺鐵球 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:20:14.000Z","msg":"新型機秒殺鐵球X<br />\nACE秒殺雜兵O"},{"pid":"3ee70e2547ec1803ad9a627c4c7cfc0c5f33a900","tid":2454771,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9cb76db2beabb199055d0ec68e08e92473778a6","tid":2454771,"uid":18012,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:06:23.000Z","msg":"海陸空都齊晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解會輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:24:05.000Z","msg":"中共海陸空都齊 <br />\n同美國打起上黎你估邊邊輸？"},{"pid":"66fb29518d246d6b484fd67aab61ee4f098b128a","tid":2454771,"uid":34377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68974055fbba7d4c2492c1dd369acda48c54bc5a","tid":2454771,"uid":34197,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"c70747a84874a4f5f109b769479bde2b01f32cd0","tid":2454771